snippet.title: Pokemon Mystery Dungeon: Amaura on the High Seas - Playthrough
snippet.description:
Broke and stuck without a job, Amaura's life has hit a new low. So she does what any logical Pokemon would do: become a pirate, of course!

Thank you to Slumbreon for creating Amaura on the High Seas and for allowing me to upload a playthrough of the game.

This is a rom hack of Pokemon Mystery Dungeon: Explorers of Sky, a.k.a. PMD: Explorers of Time & Explorers of Darkness 

Follow me on Twitter https://twitter.com/PmdGang​​ 
#MysteryDungeon​​
#Pokemon​​
#SkyTempleJam
